---
layout: "base"
title: "Bipolarer Phasenverlauf — Interaktiv | PUK Zürich"
description: "Interaktive Visualisierung des bipolaren Phasenverlaufs: Manie, Hypomanie, Euthymie und Depression im zeitlichen Zusammenhang. Für Angehörige. PUK Zürich."
permalink: "/tools/phasenverlauf/"
toolBackHref: "/modul/1/"
toolBackLabel: "Zurück zu Modul 1"
useSharedCSS: true
useNavJS: false
useToolCSS: true
bodyClass: "phasenverlauf-page"
breadcrumbs:
  - name: "Werkzeuge"
    url: "/werkzeuge/"
  - name: "Phasenverlauf"
    url: "/tools/phasenverlauf/"
---
{% block headCSS %}<!-- Phasenverlauf styles migrated to tools.css (P2.4) -->{% endblock %}
{% block nav %}
{% include "nav-tool.njk" %}
{% endblock %}
{% block content %}
<main class="wrap" id="main-content">
  <div class="hdr">
<div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Startseite</a><span class="sep" aria-hidden="true">›</span><a href="/werkzeuge/">Werkzeuge</a><span class="sep" aria-hidden="true">›</span><span>Phasenverlauf</span></div>
    <div class="tool-glyph" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path d="M5 25C10 25 10 9 16 9C22 9 22 31 28 31C32 31 32 18 35 18" stroke="var(--teal-light)" stroke-width="3.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        <circle cx="16" cy="9" r="3" fill="var(--amber-light)"/>
        <circle cx="28" cy="31" r="3" fill="var(--blue-phase)"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h1>Bipolarer Phasenverlauf</h1>
    <p>Wählen Sie eine Phase — entweder im Diagramm oder über die Schaltflächen — um zu erfahren, was sie für Betroffene und Angehörige bedeutet.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mobile-chart-note">Auf kleinen Screens ist das Diagramm ausgeblendet, damit die Seite ruhiger bleibt. Wählen Sie unten direkt eine Phase, um die Einordnung zu lesen.</div>

  <!-- Chart -->
  <div class="chart-wrap">
    <div class="chart-top">
      <span class="chart-heading">Stimmungsverlauf über die Zeit</span>
      <div class="chart-legend">
        <span class="leg"><span class="leg-dot leg-dot--mania"></span>Manie</span>
        <span class="leg"><span class="leg-dot leg-dot--hypo"></span>Hypomanie</span>
        <span class="leg"><span class="leg-dot leg-dot--stable"></span>Stabil</span>
        <span class="leg"><span class="leg-dot leg-dot--dep-mild"></span>Leichte Dep.</span>
        <span class="leg"><span class="leg-dot leg-dot--dep-severe"></span>Schwere Dep.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="chart-svg-wrap">
      <!--
        ViewBox 0 0 540 280
        5 horizontal zones (each 56px tall):
          Manie:           y   0 – 56   mid y=28
          Hypomanie:       y  56 – 112  mid y=84
          Stabil:          y 112 – 168  mid y=140
          Leichte Dep.:    y 168 – 224  mid y=196
          Schwere Dep.:    y 224 – 280  mid y=252

        Wave path (x range 90–530):
          Start  x=90,  y=140 (stabil)
          Manie  x=160, y=28
          Stabil x=230, y=140
          Schwere Dep. x=300, y=252
          Stabil x=370, y=140
          Hypo   x=430, y=84
          Stabil x=490, y=140
          Mild Dep. x=520, y=196  → end x=530, y=196
      -->
      <svg class="chart-svg" viewBox="0 0 540 280" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
           role="img" aria-label="Vereinfachter bipolarer Phasenverlauf. Interaktiv — Phasen anklicken für Details.">

        <!-- Zone backgrounds -->
        <rect x="0" y="0"   width="540" height="56"  fill="var(--amber-bg)" id="zone-mania"       class="zone-bg" data-phase="mania"/>
        <rect x="0" y="56"  width="540" height="56"  fill="var(--hypo-phase-bg)" id="zone-hypo"        class="zone-bg" data-phase="hypomania"/>
        <rect x="0" y="112" width="540" height="56"  fill="var(--success-soft)" id="zone-stable"      class="zone-bg" data-phase="stable"/>
        <rect x="0" y="168" width="540" height="56"  fill="var(--blue-phase-light)" id="zone-mild"        class="zone-bg" data-phase="mild-dep"/>
        <rect x="0" y="224" width="540" height="56"  fill="var(--severe-dep-phase-bg)" id="zone-severe"      class="zone-bg" data-phase="severe-dep"/>

        <!-- Zone separators -->
        <line x1="0" y1="56"  x2="540" y2="56"  stroke="var(--border-warm-md)" stroke-width="0.6" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/>
        <line x1="0" y1="112" x2="540" y2="112" stroke="var(--border-warm-md)" stroke-width="0.6" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/>
        <line x1="0" y1="168" x2="540" y2="168" stroke="var(--border-warm-md)" stroke-width="1"/>
        <line x1="0" y1="224" x2="540" y2="224" stroke="var(--border-warm-md)" stroke-width="0.6" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/>

        <!-- Baseline (stable midline) -->
        <line x1="80" y1="140" x2="540" y2="140" stroke="var(--phase-green)" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-dasharray="6 4" opacity="0.35"/>

        <!-- Zone labels -->
        <text x="8" y="32"  font-size="10" fill="var(--amber)" font-weight="700" font-family="DM Sans,sans-serif">Manie</text>
        <text x="8" y="88"  font-size="10" fill="var(--hypo-phase)" font-weight="700" font-family="DM Sans,sans-serif">Hypomanie</text>
        <text x="8" y="144" font-size="10" fill="var(--phase-green)" font-weight="700" font-family="DM Sans,sans-serif">Stabil</text>
        <text x="8" y="200" font-size="10" fill="var(--blue-phase)" font-weight="700" font-family="DM Sans,sans-serif">Leichte Dep.</text>
        <text x="8" y="256" font-size="10" fill="var(--slate)" font-weight="700" font-family="DM Sans,sans-serif">Schwere Dep.</text>

        <!-- Clickable zone hit areas (full width, for accessibility) -->
        <rect x="0" y="0"   width="540" height="56"  class="zone-hit" data-phase="mania"      id="hit-mania" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"/>
        <rect x="0" y="56"  width="540" height="56"  class="zone-hit" data-phase="hypomania"  id="hit-hypo" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"/>
        <rect x="0" y="112" width="540" height="56"  class="zone-hit" data-phase="stable"     id="hit-stable" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"/>
        <rect x="0" y="168" width="540" height="56"  class="zone-hit" data-phase="mild-dep"   id="hit-mild" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"/>
        <rect x="0" y="224" width="540" height="56"  class="zone-hit" data-phase="severe-dep" id="hit-severe" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"/>

        <!-- Wave path (animated in) -->
        <path id="wavePath"
          d="M 90,140 C 115,140 130,28 160,28 C 190,28 205,140 230,140 C 255,140 270,252 300,252 C 330,252 345,140 370,140 C 390,140 405,84 430,84 C 455,84 465,140 490,140 C 505,140 510,196 520,196"
          stroke="var(--teal)" stroke-width="3" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>

        <!-- Interactive wave points -->
        <circle class="wpt" cx="160" cy="28"  r="9" fill="var(--amber)" stroke="var(--card)" stroke-width="2.5" data-phase="mania"      id="pt-mania" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-label="Manie auswählen"/>
        <circle class="wpt" cx="300" cy="252" r="9" fill="var(--slate)" stroke="var(--card)" stroke-width="2.5" data-phase="severe-dep" id="pt-severe" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-label="Schwere Depression auswählen"/>
        <circle class="wpt" cx="370" cy="140" r="9" fill="var(--phase-green)" stroke="var(--card)" stroke-width="2.5" data-phase="stable"     id="pt-stable" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-label="Stabile Phase auswählen"/>
        <circle class="wpt" cx="430" cy="84"  r="9" fill="var(--hypo-phase)" stroke="var(--card)" stroke-width="2.5" data-phase="hypomania"  id="pt-hypo" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-label="Hypomanie auswählen"/>
        <circle class="wpt" cx="520" cy="196" r="9" fill="var(--blue-phase)" stroke="var(--card)" stroke-width="2.5" data-phase="mild-dep"   id="pt-mild" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-label="Leichte Depression auswählen"/>

        <!-- Pulse rings (animated) -->
        <circle cx="160" cy="28"  r="15" fill="none" stroke="var(--amber)" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0" class="pulse" id="pulse-mania"/>
        <circle cx="300" cy="252" r="15" fill="none" stroke="var(--slate)" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0" class="pulse" id="pulse-severe"/>
        <circle cx="370" cy="140" r="15" fill="none" stroke="var(--phase-green)" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0" class="pulse" id="pulse-stable"/>
        <circle cx="430" cy="84"  r="15" fill="none" stroke="var(--hypo-phase)" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0" class="pulse" id="pulse-hypo"/>
        <circle cx="520" cy="196" r="15" fill="none" stroke="var(--blue-phase)" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0" class="pulse" id="pulse-mild"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <p class="chart-xlab">Zeit (vereinfacht — Episodenabstände variieren stark, von Wochen bis Jahren)</p>
  </div>

  <p class="hint">Klicken Sie auf einen Punkt im Diagramm oder wählen Sie eine Phase:</p>

  <!-- Phase selector buttons -->
  <div class="phase-btns" role="group" aria-label="Phase auswählen">
    <button type="button" class="pbtn" data-phase="mania"      aria-pressed="false"><span class="ico">↑↑</span>Manie</button>
    <button type="button" class="pbtn" data-phase="hypomania"  aria-pressed="false"><span class="ico">↑</span>Hypomanie</button>
    <button type="button" class="pbtn" data-phase="stable"     aria-pressed="false"><span class="ico">→</span>Stabil</button>
    <button type="button" class="pbtn" data-phase="mild-dep"   aria-pressed="false"><span class="ico">↓</span>Leichte Dep.</button>
    <button type="button" class="pbtn" data-phase="severe-dep" aria-pressed="false"><span class="ico">↓↓</span>Schwere Dep.</button>
  </div>

  <!-- Detail card -->
  <div class="detail-card" id="detailCard" aria-live="polite"></div>
  <noscript>
    <div class="noscript-box">
      <p>Die interaktive Visualisierung benötigt JavaScript.</p>
      <p>Die Phasen und ihre Bedeutung finden Sie auch in <a href="/modul/1/">Modul 1</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </noscript>

</main>
{% endblock %}
{% block footer %}
{% include "footer-medium.njk" %}
{% endblock %}
{% block scripts %}
<script src="/js/tool-phasenverlauf.js"></script>
{% endblock %}
